-- TABLE-Euro-zone M3 growth slows in April, private loans contract
-- 
-- Wed May 28, 2014 04:15AM EDT
-- None



FRANKFURT, May 28 (Reuters) - Lending to households and firms in the euro zone declined further in April and money supply growth slowed, the European Central Bank said on Wednesday.

